1. After activating various Heavenly Dao, the game will trigger a certain Heavenly chaos according to the dictates of the Heavenly Dao, thereby changing the game content.
2. Chaos are divided into 3 types: a. Constant: Choose one of three specific effects, which will permanently take effect in this game.

Obtain energy to nurture the Purple Jade Tablet through weekly and seasonal tasks, thereby enhancing its level. The energy required for each level of the Purple Jade Tablet is fixed.

Seasons are a new activity gameplay introduced in the mobile version. A new season starts at regular intervals, each offering new gameplay mechanics and unique seasonal appearances. The Purple Jade Tablet is the core of the season. Complete weekly and seasonal tasks to obtain energy and nurture the Jade Tablet. Each level increase allows you to claim corresponding rewards. In addition to the Jade Tablet rewards, the season offers three new game modes: ---【Season】,【Challenge】,【Extreme】 Playing in these modes is essential for seasonal gameplay and provides a different experience from the Classic mode. In the 【Challenge】 and 【Extreme】 modes, you automatically compete in the Three Realms Ranking. Note: Jade Tablet level, weekly tasks, seasonal tasks, and ranking data reset at the end of the season. New content arrives in the next season!

Although the company's development costs are considerable, we hope to earn some revenue through the mobile game. However, we want to remind everyone, especially players new to [Cultivation Mobile Game]. Except for the expansion packs (DLC), the other paid content is not very cost-effective and can mostly be obtained through in-game operations and skills.
We are happier to see everyone fully understanding and enjoying the game. So please purchase cautiously. If you still choose to purchase, it would be a strong support for the development of the cultivation series products, and the entire development team sincerely thanks you!

The ancient dragon forbidden area of Longtai reappeared. People went to look for opportunities. But no one expected that the formation used to seal the fierce Phoenix, the great enemy of the dragon clan, had also been inadvertently destroyed by people who knew nothing about it. It is said that the fierce Phoenix was originally a auspicious beast in ancient times. After killing and robbing, it became nirvana. After waking up again, it was already in a frenzy. Its fierce power was unparalleled. It even ate dragons. It was also the most fierce existence in ancient times when there were many strong people. Now the fierce Phoenix is recovering again. 1. After enabling various Heavenly Dao, the game will trigger a specific Heavenly Chaos according to the rules of the Heavenly Dao, thereby changing the game content.
2. Types of chaos: Constant: Choose one of three specific effects. Turbulent: Choose one condition and one effect from four sets, combining them into a complete chaotic effect. Yin-Yang: Choose one Yin effect and one Yang effect from four sets, combining them into a complete chaotic effect.
3. Degrees of chaos: Shallow Layer: The Heavenly Chaos effect disappears after the trigger count is exhausted. Middle Layer: The Heavenly Chaos effect is effective during the duration. Deep Layer: The acquired Heavenly Chaos effect is permanent in this game round.
